{"tid":405546,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"可否加個report function?","createTime":"2017-09-19T02:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T09:27:27.000Z","uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ddcc2e15006438d0c480f41c479af142700d830","tid":405546,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:38:15.000Z","msg":"我知連登畀人ddos緊大家都好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我覺提升lihkg 既品質一樣重要<br />\n<br />\n可否加個report function<br />\n<br />\nreport 多過 N 既人出啲post 自動隱藏而且有警告，要睇個啲可以click 佢打開<br />\n<br />\nthanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c25c9154547c11814edc795adbe0cfe7a2ffcf","tid":405546,"uid":58358,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:45:03.000Z","msg":"pseudo code:<br />\n<br />\nfor post in posts<br />\n  if post.owner.num_reports_received &gt; n<br />\n    post.content_hidden = True <br />\n    post.message = &quot;This user has received too many reports .... &quot;<br />\n  else<br />\n    display(post)"},{"pid":"a84b157e080b69269a501ce8d1d5d04ac32593ce","tid":405546,"uid":122576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User"},{"pid":"10f774496a0753713113c7c1a6d433b77d3fe9bc","tid":405546,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/130002_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F130002_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4553a374&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2af41ede3507864c019076547e3078aa01edd038","tid":405546,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"推到 admin 見到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162e74f101cf513e